{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/blog/javascript/[2022-09-05 02] moment UTC/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>날짜 관련해서 헷갈리는 부분을 정리해보았다.</p>\n<p>GMT란 <code>Greenwich Mean Time</code>의 약어로 그리니치 평균시를 뜻한다.<br>\n영군 런던에 소재한 그리니치 천문대를 기점으로 정했다. GMT(+0)</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>GMT+0은 Z로 표기한다. (Zulu Time)<br>\n한국은 <code>GMT+9</code> 이다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>UTC(<code>Universal Time Coordinated</code>)는 협정 세계시를 뜻한다.<br>\nUTC는 GMT에 기반하므로 GMT라 불리기도 하는데<br>\n기술적인 표기로 <code>UTC</code>가 맞다.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>실제 UTC와 GMT의 차이는 밀리초정도만 차이난다.<br>\n한국은 <code>UTC+9</code> 이다. (GMT와 동일)</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2>애매모호한 부분</h2>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container abyss grvsc-ps-t4tStz\" data-language=\"js\" data-index=\"0\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-15 grvsc-t9ljLd-i grvsc-t4tStz-3\">console</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">.</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-15 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">log</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">(</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-7 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">new</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> </span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-5 grvsc-t9ljLd-u grvsc-t4tStz-1\">Date</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">(</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-11 grvsc-t4tStz-10\">&quot;2022-09-05&quot;</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">).</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-6 grvsc-t4tStz-5\">toISOString</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">()) </span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-3 grvsc-t4tStz-2\">// 2022-09-05T00:00:00.000Z // UTC+0</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-15 grvsc-t9ljLd-i grvsc-t4tStz-3\">console</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">.</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-15 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">log</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">(</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-7 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">new</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> </span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-5 grvsc-t9ljLd-u grvsc-t4tStz-1\">Date</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">(</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-11 grvsc-t4tStz-10\">&quot;2022/09/05&quot;</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">).</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-6 grvsc-t4tStz-5\">toISOString</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">()) </span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-3 grvsc-t4tStz-2\">// 2022-09-04T15:00:00.000Z // localTime</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>파싱할 문자열에 UTC 정보가 없을 경우, <code>-</code>으로 구분하냐 <code>/</code>으로 구분하냐에 따라 시간대 정보가 다르게 출력된다.</p>\n<p>ISO 표준은 UTC 관련정보가 없으면(Z 또는 +00:00)<br>\n<code>local time</code>으로 가정한다고 나와있다. (<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_8601#Local_time_(unqualified)\">ISO_8601</a>)</p>\n<p>하지만 ES5에선 <code>UTC+0</code>로 가정한다.</p>\n<p>하이픈(<code>-</code>)으로 구분된 문자는 되도록 ECMA 표준을 따르지만 그 외에는 ISO 표준을 따르고 있다.</p>\n<p>이런 부분이 애매모호해서 그런지<br>\n<code>moment.js</code>에서는 <code>-</code>이든 <code>/</code>이든 ISO 기준으로 출력한다. (UTC 정보가 없을 경우 Local Time 기준으로)</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container abyss grvsc-ps-t4tStz\" data-language=\"js\" data-index=\"1\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-15 grvsc-t9ljLd-i grvsc-t4tStz-3\">console</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">.</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-15 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">log</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">(</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-6 grvsc-t4tStz-5\">moment</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">(</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-11 grvsc-t4tStz-10\">&quot;2022-09-05&quot;</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">).</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-6 grvsc-t4tStz-5\">format</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">()) </span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-3 grvsc-t4tStz-2\">// 2022-09-05T00:00:00+09:00</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-15 grvsc-t9ljLd-i grvsc-t4tStz-3\">console</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">.</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-15 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">log</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">(</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-6 grvsc-t4tStz-5\">moment</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">(</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-11 grvsc-t4tStz-10\">&quot;2022/09/05&quot;</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">).</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-6 grvsc-t4tStz-5\">format</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">()) </span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-3 grvsc-t4tStz-2\">// 2022-09-05T00:00:00+09:00</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>다만 <code>UTC+0</code> 기준으로 표기하고 싶을 때엔 <code>utc</code>를 활용한다.</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container abyss grvsc-ps-t4tStz\" data-language=\"js\" data-index=\"2\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-15 grvsc-t9ljLd-i grvsc-t4tStz-3\">console</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">.</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-15 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">log</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">(moment.</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-6 grvsc-t4tStz-5\">utc</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">(</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-11 grvsc-t4tStz-10\">&quot;2022-09-05&quot;</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">).</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-6 grvsc-t4tStz-5\">format</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">()) </span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-3 grvsc-t4tStz-2\">// 2022-09-05T00:00:00Z</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><code>local time</code>으로 표기된 정보를 <code>utc</code> 기준으로 보고 싶을 경우에는</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container abyss grvsc-ps-t4tStz\" data-language=\"js\" data-index=\"3\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-15 grvsc